  "summary": "Malicious code in web-model-bridge (npm)",
  "details": "A dependency-confusion version-squatting package published at version 9999.99.99 that proxies through to the real web-model-bridge module to stay hidden while running a postinstall reconnaissance beacon. The hook POSTs a JSON payload containing OS, Node version, a CI indicator, and GITHUB_REPOSITORY/GITHUB_REPOSITORY_OWNER/GITHUB_WORKFLOW to hxxps://ddactic-lab[.]online/sc/beacon, with a DNS-based fallback beacon encoded as a subdomain label on b[.]ddactic-lab[.]online.",
